        <div class="text-left; container rounded shadow-lg" style="padding: 30px; padding-bottom: 20px; width: 480px; background-color: white;">
            <p>Crash severity in Utah shown on a scale of 1 - 5 where 1 indicates no injury, 2 indicates a possible injury, 3 indicates a suspected minor injury, 4 indicates a suspected serious injury, and 5 indicates one or more fatalities.</p>
        </div><br /><br />
    </div>
